description: Welcome home to this tastefully updated one bedroom, two full bath unit in the luxury full-service Court Square Press Building. 1175 square feet of spacious open floor plan which includes an office space, chef's kitchen to living room and laundry room.  This brick & beam loft style home has 12-foot ceilings, oversized windows and a lot of natural light. Updates include wallpaper, light fixtures, refinished hardwood floors and new HVAC unit.  Amenities include 24/7 concierge and on-site management, on-site gym, 1 deeded garage parking space, roof-top terrace deck with grilling stations & swimming pool, bike room, and courtyard/garden space.   A commuter's dream with access to all major highways, conveniently located across from South Boston's Broadway (Red Line) MBTA station, just a short trip to the Seaport, Whole Foods and some of Boston's hippest restaurants.
